OL,4,G1435FOutback Truckers
OL,5,     GIn the Northern Territory the wet
OL,6,     Gseason's about to break and
OL,7,     Gveteran road train trucker Mark
OL,8,     GPett is hauling 78 tonnes of
OL,9,     Gcement and steel straight into a
OL,10,     Gdisaster zone.
OL,11,G1530FOutback Truckers
OL,12,     G20 year veteran trucker Yogi is
OL,13,     Gon a mercy mission leading a hay
OL,14,     Gconvoy to the drought ravaged
OL,15,     Gfarmers of New South Wales.
